  "short_text": "Kilometers to Meters",
  "content": "Write a program to take the number of kilometers as input and convert into meters and print the number of meters.<br/>Note: 1 Kilometer = 1000 Meters<hr><b>Input</b><br/><br/>The first line of input contains the number of kilometers.<br/>The input will have a decimal part.<hr><b>Output</b><br/><br/>The first line of output contains the number of meters.<br/>The output should be an integer.<hr><b>Explanation</b><br/><br/>For example, 1.2 kilometers is equals to 1200 meters",
